metadata.name: Walking In The Wild
metadata.description:
Her heart is wild,
World is a wild mystery,
Life is a mystery too,
But she dares to take a walk in this wild mystery,
Watching out every step that she takes here,
it can yield her a treat,
or you never know it might be a trap,
But she takes it anyway.
Do you dare to walk along with her in this wild journey?

Artist : Sahana (@sahiscraftworld)
Photographer : Naman (@Cryptogod_Naman)

This NFT is minted as part of Cryptogod's World 2.0 : Fusion of Photography x NFT.

Cryptogod's World project is a unique collaboration of 150+ Artists & Photographers. We are bringing together the magic of photography & art to create 1/1 Fusion NFTs.
